				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "h0yznn37DQCV04pCDqFdyA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "In this blog post, I outline some principles I see as immutable, regardless of system shape, and explain why I hold these beliefs. I explain what views I—and probably you—need. And finally, we talk a bit about how to produce it while acknowledging that this is dependent on which technologies you use."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-09-18T19:58:30.806836-05:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-09-18T20:00:01.952878-05:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "jqaMtH77DQC/4xglDqFdyA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The point isn’t to generate pretty pictures; in fact, I couldn’t care less about the layout or color scheme (okay, okay, readability would be nice). I want truthfulness and having to memorize a bunch of verbal addenda and errata when I meet with the architect for the first time."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
