				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-09-18T19:06:48.997381-05:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "1ob97X37DQCm83XtDqFdyA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "- **Context:** external actors, major systems, trust boundaries.\n- **Container:** services, data stores, queues, external SaaS.\n- **Component:** internals of the service (for your most critical services).\n- **Data flow:** data flows, classifications, trust zone crossings. Think DFD.\n- **Network segmentation:** VPC/VNet, subnets, SG/NSG/NetworkPolicy edges, ingress/egress points.\n- **Auth flows:** OIDC/OAuth exchanges, token scopes, service-to-service auth.\n- **Data persistence:** stores, retention, RPO/RTO, backup/restore, encryption.\n- **Runtime topology:** deployment graph (K8s namespaces, workloads, ingresses)."
			},
