				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I know that some of these are easier to generate than others, and creating all of these accurately and automatically isn’t always feasible. This is a best-in-class write-up, and for some systems might remain aspirational. Try to get as close to it as possible (and then back off when the asymptotes kick in)."
